description:
The Breakfast Club is dropping keys and some of their favorite interviews of 2016! Today's show features DJ Khaled, "Da Snowman" Jeezy, Bill Simmons and Issa Rae of HBO's "Insecure." Plus, Jaheim and Ryan Lochte prove why they're candidates for Donkey of the Year.
